                "actions": {
                    "value": "2"
                },
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The vargouille shrieks, its scream so terrible that all non-vargouilles within 60 feet must succeed at a <span data-pf2-check=\"fortitude\" data-pf2-dc=\"16\" data-pf2-traits=\"auditory,concentrate,visual\" data-pf2-label=\"Shriek DC\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">Fortitude</span> save<em data-visibility=\"gm\"> or be @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Paralyzed]{Paralyzed} for 3 rounds</em>.</p>\n<p><em data-visibility=\"gm\">The effect ends early for a creature if the vargouille moves out of sight, moves farther than 60 feet from the creature, or attacks the creature with its fangs.</em></p>\n<p><em data-visibility=\"gm\">After attempting its save, a creature is immune to that particular vargouille's Shriek for 24 hours.</em></p>"
